    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>301680</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_080_017&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>くっ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ugh...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>301880</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_080_018&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ディオスは……
いや……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Dios really...no...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>301880</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_080_019&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>オレらはずっと
思ってたんだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I've been thinking hard about it.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>301880</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_080_020&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ダオスがもっと、
しっかりしていれば、
戦争は起きなかったって</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Had you ruled in a different way, the
war would have never happened.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302092</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_080_021&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>筋違いってわかってた。
でも、わたしたちは勝手に
あなたを恨みに思ってました</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I know it sounds absurd...but we
held deep resentment towards you.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302092</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_080_022&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そんなわたしたちの想いを
あなたはひとりで背負い
苦悩してたんですね</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>But we didn't know you had to bear
so many painful things on your own...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302396</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_080_025&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>もはや葛藤など捨てた</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I no longer wish to fight.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302548</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_080_026&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>今のあなたの存在、それが
葛藤の徴（しるし）……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Your existence right now...it embodies grief...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302548</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_080_027&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>その葛藤があなたの
優しさの証……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>And that mourning is a sign of your kindness...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302752</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_080_028&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……オレらもちゃんと
自分の罪に向き合う</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...We need to face our sins, too.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302752</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_080_029&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あんたが不安に向き合って、
戦い続けたのと同じで</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You had to keep on fighting,
despite feeling conflicted.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>302752</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_080_030&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>オレらもちゃんと決着をつける</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We need to set things right.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303312</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_080_031&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>……私はおまえたちの行ったことを
取り返せるとは思わぬ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...I did not expect you to genuinely
seek retribution for your sins.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303312</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_080_032&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>我が星、デリス・カーラーンは
滅びの危機を迎えた</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I was forced to accept the annihilation
of my dear home planet, Derris Kharlan.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303312</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_080_033&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そして私自身は、自分の怒り、
憎しみ、慢心……自分の心に
敗北し息絶えたのだ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>And then inside of me arose a myriad of
overwhelming emotions... Shock, sadness,
anger... It was then that my heart died.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303312</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_080_034&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>この世に悪と呼べるものが
あるとすれば、それは人の心だ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>If there is evil in this world,
it lurks in the hearts of men.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>3</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303312</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_080_035&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そして、最も恐るべきもの。
勝たねばならない敵……
それが自分の心だ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That is a dreadful truth. My heart...it
became an insurmountable opponent.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>4</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303312</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_080_036&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>おまえたちは、
自分から分かれた自分の心と
向き合っている</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You have come here of your own
accord to face my lingering feelings.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>5</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303312</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_080_037&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>決着をつけるがよい。
おまえたちの大罪の始末を</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>So you wish to right your wrongs. You will
acknowledge and atone for your sins...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>13</Id>
      <BubbleId>6</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303368</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_080_038&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ああ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Aah...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>20</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303448</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_080_039&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>戻ろうぜ、
オレらの時代に</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Let's go back to our time.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>21</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303616</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_080_041&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ディオスとメルティアは
&lt;Red&gt;審理の晶谷&lt;White&gt;にいるよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Dios and Meltia are at
the &lt;Red&gt;Crystal Valley of Judgment&lt;White&gt;.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>22</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303688</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_080_042&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Red&gt;審理の晶谷&lt;White&gt;……？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Red&gt;Crystal Valley of Judgment&lt;White&gt;...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>5</SpeakerId>
      <Id>23</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303764</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_080_043&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>&lt;Rody&gt;はどうするの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>&lt;Rody&gt;...what will you do?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>24</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303940</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_080_044&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>私も一緒に行く</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm coming too.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>25</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303940</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_080_045&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>君たちの罪の行方
見守るって言ったでしょ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I did say I'd look after you
while you make your amends.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>25</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>303940</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_080_046&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>私の知りたかった
色んなこと……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>All of the things I wanted to know...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>25</Id>
      <BubbleId>2</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>304036</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_080_047&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>双子ちゃんのおかげで
知ることができたから</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's thanks to you two that I figured it all out.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>28</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>304264</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_080_050&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>ありがと、ダオス……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Thank you. Dhaos...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>29</Id>
      <BubbleId>0</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>304264</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VSM_310_080_051&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>さようなら</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>And goodbye...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>29</Id>
      <BubbleId>1</BubbleId>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>304308</PointerOffset>
      <JapaneseText>…………</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>31</Id>
      <Status>Proofreading</Status>
    </Entry>
